{
  "text": "The method of proof follows the general outline in the notes of Bakry [CITATION_1] . Define the Jacobi differential operator L to be Lf = (1 \u2212 x 2 )f \u2032\u2032 (x) + (q \u2212 p \u2212 (p + q)x)f \u2032 (x), and define the carr\u00e9 du champ operator \u0393 by",
